{"tid":1481534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國泰員工不忿白色恐怖 發公開信寄語港人背水一戰：8.18維園見！","createTime":"2019-08-17T17:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T23:30:31.000Z","uid":68738,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c7d41673260cc44266d86cbd863a622170c35935","tid":1481534,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190817/large/1566043197_c51b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190817%2Flarge%2F1566043197_c51b.jpg&h=368d56bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190817/large/1566047814_7c6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190817%2Flarge%2F1566047814_7c6c.jpg&h=cefb4a52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國泰航空遭中共窮追猛打。一群國泰員工今日發出公開信，批評國家機器全方位針對航空公司進行政治打壓，更利用白色恐怖來摧毁言論自由。其中一名發起人表示，公開信中特別引用獅子山精神，希望港人和國泰員工都能同舟共濟，不割席、不分化，更不畏懼，堅持齊上齊落的信念，「明天，維園見」。<br />\n<br />\n逆權運動持續兩個月，中共接連向國泰航空施壓，先是中國民航局針對國泰發出重大航空安全風險警示，逼使國泰解僱兩名機師，其後行政總裁何杲與顧客及商務總裁盧家培也「被辭職」，國泰內部已瀰漫一片白色恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n一群國泰航空集團員工今日發出《致香港人書》，指出過去兩個多月，有逾 30 次集會、無間斷的十八區遊行，以及歷史性罷工等，已有超過200萬人發聲。但政府未有正面回應市民，反而施放逾1,800枚催淚彈、暴力拘捕逾700名抗爭者，「運動中重傷流血、骨折失明的，不計其數」。<br />\n<br />\n信中指出，雖然近日民眾力量已成功三度令機場停擺，引起國際高度關注，但國家機器開始全方位針對航空公司，進行政治打壓；假借飛行安全迫令公司解僱支持抗爭者的員工，利用白色恐怖來摧毁言論自由，更不擇手段令公司表態及高層「被辭職」。<br />\n<br />\n「當香港的優良制度被蠶食、言論及集會自由被剝削，香港將不再是香港」。信中指出，獅子山精神從來都不是代表「收成期」的黃金時代，而是每一代人不屈不撓、齊上齊落的堅毅信念，「各位香港人，我們已退無可退。下跪求饒不能絕處逢生，相反拼死一搏才可浴火重生」。信末重申五大訴求，缺一不可，包括落實雙普選、撤回惡法和暴動定性、成立獨立調查委員會及釋放所有反送中被捕者。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名發起人受訪時表示，逆權運動爆發至今逾兩個月，香港人面對不同程度的打壓，故特別引用獅子山精神，藉此勉勵港人毋忘初衷，就是不割席、不分化，就算走過幾許苦難，若能同舟共濟，深信最終都能成就事件。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，當下的香港被白色恐怖籠罩，國泰更甚，希望能藉《致香港人書》，鼓勵香港人和國泰員工走出恐懼，出席明天在維園的集會，向國家機器的打壓說不，「香港人絕不投降」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190817/59943846?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190817%2F59943846%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1KjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=671c7dc4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190817%2F59943846%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=f6a01d54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190817/59943846?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"35d341617d6c818f6b336daacbcde19d11e6ff22","tid":1481534,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:55:41.000Z","msg":"【突發】英國紀錄片導演想搵人傾下香港人嘅故事，下年喺美國PBS同英國Channel 4廣播！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1481499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1481499</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"daa3a043aa436ade72c2c7f86981af24674749be","tid":1481534,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:00:56.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n818維園見！所有聽日去嘅人都同我入一入嚟！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1480894\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1480894</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a33f8d48a18c5c08bb7b925d569eec15e45c4cff","tid":1481534,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb0ddbee2290e4ce225bc371fdb661be8225217","tid":1481534,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:07:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀~"},{"pid":"9de31c48395a905ce2b63c6c5ac4c4f5b0da5306","tid":1481534,"uid":79278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:11:30.000Z","msg":"咁高調會玩死國泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ddfefacad2da86373eec21e55bdfab59f74933","tid":1481534,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:15:06.000Z","msg":"唔知真定假, 但好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(未FC)中共民航局要求交罷工名單，國泰CEO只交左自己個名！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dFMPRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dFMPRS</a>"},{"pid":"6c5554862d4c1fa5bfe20d43ed9f16c5e1896f7a","tid":1481534,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T20:04:44.000Z","msg":"如果我去旅行我一定唔坐國泰航空<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441386/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441386/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"de1214b768b71f70b9b4cff5ee40f8bdc0fbbe22","tid":1481534,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T20:05:02.000Z","msg":"抵制係一種態度<br />\n抵制係兩邊力量的較量<br />\n抵制係兩邊在拔河<br />\n看政權向企業施加的限制有效還是消費者更有效"},{"pid":"54d87b39e15d019c747933091fda18fc9421152d","tid":1481534,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T20:05:15.000Z","msg":"國泰大股東係咪中資<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇5毛就知道"},{"pid":"7c8de46d0510c0a33a52cc8ee7f056eba0127e9e","tid":1481534,"uid":289846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T20:05:40.000Z","msg":"國泰航空：CEO在香港「反送中」風暴中「引咎辭職」<br />\n良心 CEO被政權迫走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc3417075bc910181064ca9f764375d032a3d26","tid":1481534,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T20:05:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TPcwfby.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTPcwfby.png&h=8aa86117&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfa8a007601ac098944430f30cfb478856f92abd","tid":1481534,"uid":194745,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:04:28.000Z","msg":"國泰不嬲好嘅只係啲機師空姐，國泰航空間公司同管理層不嬲對機師空姐極差，只因有機師空姐工會幫佢哋。啲管理層只是吸血蛀米大蟲，吸盡機師同空姐的工作成果。<br />\n<br />\n啲管理層炒燃油對沖蝕錢，就搵員工裁員找數。自己亂駛錢大花筒就刻薄空姐，減航班人手加座位。<br />\n<br />\n大家要分開公司同員工，pacific place啲員工幫手，唔代表太古幫手。太古不嬲都是奶共㗎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">啲管理層已經將員工名單交給民航局，嗰啲示過威表過態嘅黃絲空姐機師冇得飛越中國領空，好快會被迫走，成間公司上上下下管理層機師空姐都會係藍絲。<br />\n<br />\n太古一早已經奶共，當初自願將國泰股權交出媚共自保，繼續揾銀。反而怡和遷冊撤出香港。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/86420\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Fmain%2F86420&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1KjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=1546bb2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/86420</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新CEO 鄧生來自港機工程，一早紮根厦門，一定好識做</span></span><br />\n<br />\n去台灣，長榮/中華<br />\n<br />\n去日本， JAL ANA PEACH<br />\n<br />\n去歐洲 英航，三寶, virgin Air France lufthansa<br />\n<br />\n去澳洲 virgin qantas<br />\n<br />\n去美國 AA United<br />\n<br />\n去中國  冇計 國泰港龍"},{"pid":"49b43e36c0bc543a62df3b47503299a5aaa6afdb","tid":1481534,"uid":194745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:23:36.000Z","msg":"上周六網上流傳一篇「國泰航空集團員工致香港人書」，一群聲稱是國泰員工指內地政治打壓令高層「被辭職」。<br />\n<br />\n國泰航空昨日發出聲明，指留意到網上傳聞，雖然暫時無法證實是否與國泰員工有關，但公司高度重視正展開調查，重申堅決支持港府、行政長官和香港警方，譴責非法活動和暴力行為。<br />\n<br />\n支持港府警方 譴責暴力<br />\n<br />\n國泰聲明重申，對近期發生在港的暴力和破壞活動深表憂慮，堅決支持特區政府、行政長官和香港警方在止暴制亂、恢復法律秩序所做出的不懈努力，又譴責一切挑戰一國兩制原則和基本法權威的非法活動和暴力行為，務必立即行動起來，反對暴力，恢復安寧，維護香港的繁榮穩定。<br />\n<br />\n聲明又指，國泰會完全遵守中國民用航空局的安全指示，亦會遵守香港民航處及航班飛往及飛越所有地區的相關法規。"},{"pid":"f1dc672fffc11d79c7370450f72d9e975f2aaa3b","tid":1481534,"uid":89834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:25:57.000Z","msg":"又可以炒多一班空姐出黎做"},{"pid":"9820b57402f53d8565acb17eba9875c55f193a7e","tid":1481534,"uid":161160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49b43e36c0bc543a62df3b47503299a5aaa6afdb","tid":1481534,"uid":194745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:23:36.000Z","msg":"上周六網上流傳一篇「國泰航空集團員工致香港人書」，一群聲稱是國泰員工指內地政治打壓令高層「被辭職」。<br />\n<br />\n國泰航空昨日發出聲明，指留意到網上傳聞，雖然暫時無法證實是否與國泰員工有關，但公司高度重視正展開調查，重申堅決支持港府、行政長官和香港警方，譴責非法活動和暴力行為。<br />\n<br />\n支持港府警方 譴責暴力<br />\n<br />\n國泰聲明重申，對近期發生在港的暴力和破壞活動深表憂慮，堅決支持特區政府、行政長官和香港警方在止暴制亂、恢復法律秩序所做出的不懈努力，又譴責一切挑戰一國兩制原則和基本法權威的非法活動和暴力行為，務必立即行動起來，反對暴力，恢復安寧，維護香港的繁榮穩定。<br />\n<br />\n聲明又指，國泰會完全遵守中國民用航空局的安全指示，亦會遵守香港民航處及航班飛往及飛越所有地區的相關法規。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:30:31.000Z","msg":"又炒車"}]}